4. We have to create new 4 receipt types (same translation in ENG+GER):
 * “Geringwertige Wirtschaftsgüter (GWG)”;
 * “Verbrauchsmaterial”;
 * “Überstellungen”;
 * “EDV Kosten”

Effective date: 15.05.2023

Thank you in advance!

Best regards,

Milosz

